data.description: Welcome to this spacious 3-bedroom, 3-bath haven spanning 2,636 sq. ft. with Large walk in closet in the main bedroom, complete with a convenient 2-car garage. Situated in a highly sought-after area, this home offers a perfect blend of elegance and practicality. Move-in ready, it provides a comfortable living experience with the added opportunity for personalization. While the property is primed for immediate occupancy, a few updates to lighting and two of the bathrooms would allow you to infuse your unique style into this already charming space. Embrace the chance to make this residence uniquely yours, situated in an idyllic locale that combines convenience and comfort.
